Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.81,0:00:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好美鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 新来的姐姐怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你问我怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(648,45)}姐姐扫描
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,朋君的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.11,0:00:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(648,45)}真的很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}漂亮不就好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就先写普通君（暂定）吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我虽然亲戚很多 但是是独生子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,她在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人…真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的数学课真是烦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天网游的怪物真强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}喂 你是哪里的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我是来找朋君的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要擅自进来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,因为父亲再婚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来了个奇怪的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:41.39,TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\pos(500,444)}心跳♡2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:41.39,TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\pos(568,526)}来学校了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 水原君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,藤咲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,藤咲简直就像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,纯白的天使一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,臣服在我的可爱之下吧 男生们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,切开后其实是纯黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:00:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,朋君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘带了便当 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她是水原的姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还是美女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,败北…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 要没别的事的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,水原君原来是有姐姐的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快给我回去 水原
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 诶诶诶 难道说那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢朋君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这个女人在瞪着我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,难道对藤咲…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,朋也喜欢藤咲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我并没有喜欢藤咲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,也完全没觉得她可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好了快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,水原这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不可爱还真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,被藤咲讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来朋君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 教室里那个女孩是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:01:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟到学校来到底打算干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细一想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她是来给我送便当的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,总感觉 真正差劲的是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,朋君对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 刚才对不起了
